OL,3,CChild has life-threatening injuries
OL,4,Cafter being hit by a car
OL,6,FA child is in hospital with life
OL,7,Fthreatening injuries after being hit
OL,8,Fby a car in Bristol.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to the junction
OL,11,Fof Long Cross and Kings Weston Road,
OL,12,Fin the Lawrence Weston area of the
OL,13,Fcity, just before 2 o'clock in the
OL,14,Fafternoon, Sunday 17 November.
OL,16,FThe two people who were in a BMW car
OL,17,Fleft the scene. An 18-year-old has
OL,18,Fsince been arrested on suspicion of
OL,19,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,20,Fdriving and driving whilst unfit
OL,21,Fthrough drink or drugs.
