OL,6,FParamedics from South Western
OL,7,FAmbulance Trust were also sent to the
OL,8,Fscene, along with Avon Fire and Rescue
OL,9,FService.
OL,11,FAvon & Somerset Police said: "We were
OL,12,Fcalled to a report that a BMW car had
OL,13,Fleft the road in Long Cross, near its
OL,14,Fjunction with Kings Weston Road, and
OL,15,Fcollided with a child. It was also
OL,16,Freported that the two occupants of the
OL,17,Fcar had subsequently left the scene."
