OL,3,CChild has life-threatening injuries
OL,4,Cafter being hit by a car
OL,6,FDetectives are appealing for
OL,7,Finformation to identify a woman as
OL,8,Fpart of their investigation. She is
OL,9,Fdescribed as white with blond hair.
OL,10,FShe was wearing a black puffer coat,
OL,11,Fblue jeans and light-coloured shoes.
OL,13,FWitnesses are asked to call 101 and
OL,14,Fgive the call handler the reference
OL,15,F5224303111. Officers are also keen to
OL,16,Fhear from anyone who may have CCTV
OL,17,Ffootage or dashcam pictures of the
OL,18,Fincident.
